  "body": "\r\n## chainId returns 31337 instead of '1' while forking mainnet. \r\n\r\n### I tried different ways of returning chainId but they all failed to return the correct number. \r\n\r\n```js \r\n\r\nfunction getChainId() external view returns (uint chainId) {\r\n        assembly {\r\n            chainId := chainid()\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function getChainId() external view returns (uint chainId) {\r\n        return block.chainid;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function getChainId() external returns (uint chainId) {\r\n        return block.chainid;\r\n    }\r\n  \r\nconst chainId = await ethers.provider.getNetwork(); \r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
